Reviews.original: The artwork effectively uses contrasting colors to enhance visual interest. The bright yellow and red of the house stand out against the more muted tones of the dog and the green blanket. The bowl of food also uses a contrasting yellow and orange, which draws attention to it. The black and white dog provides a stark contrast to the colorful background, making it a focal point of the piece. However, the contrast could be slightly more pronounced in some areas to achieve a more striking visual impact.
